Mechel, Novorossiysk, Russian Sea: Russian Equities Preview

-- B y   S t e p h e n   B i e r m a n
-- 
2011-06-28T20:01:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-28/mechel-novorossiysk-russian-sea-russian-equities-preview.html
The following companies may be
active in Russian trading. Stock symbols are in parentheses and
share prices are from the previous close of trading in Moscow.  The 30-stock Micex Index rose 1.5 percent to 1,651.50. The
dollar-denominated RTS Index climbed 1.7 percent to 1,874.34.  OAO  Mechel (MTLR)  :  Russia ’s largest miner of steelmaking
coal plans to release first-quarter financial results at 10 a.m.
local time. The stock gained 1.5 percent to 718.4 rubles.  OAO Novorossiysk Commercial Sea Port (NMTP RX): The company
plans to announce first-quarter financial results at 10 a.m.
local time. Shares in Russia’s largest commercial seaport rose
1.7 percent to 3.396 rubles in Moscow.  OAO  Russian Sea Group (RSEA)  : Billionaire investor
 Gennady Timchenko ’s Volga Resources investment fund has agreed
to acquire a stake in the food producer through a venture with
RS Group. The consumer food producer rose 2.5 percent to 69.33
rubles in Moscow.  To contact the reporter on this story:
